        "client_msg_id": "7c9efdfd-bb95-4038-afc2-b9fff51cb570",
        "type": "message",
        "text": "In some sense, it's already a very popular model today, via _dependency injection_, where you explicitly pass in specific services that some code needs, rather than having that functionality gloabally available. Object capabilities essentially takes this programming\n pattern to its logical conclusion, and uses it as the security model as well.",
